skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Welcome to Hello DFW! The news cycle is negative, overwhelming, and repetitive. We'll do our best to feature some of the most interesting (and hopefully positive) stories of the week without burning you out. Tune in every Wednesday to learn something new about your community!

The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
